This paper is primarily focused on face detection and recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for these tasks, which could place it in the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the need for improved algorithms for open-set face recognition, which could place it in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The use of surveillance cameras and the challenges they present could also place this paper in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the need for improved security measures, which could place it in the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
